{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place parsley into mixing bowl and chop <b>3 sec\/speed 7<b>. Transfer into a bowl and set aside.","Place water into mixing bowl. Place mussels into Varoma dish, place Varoma into position, secure Varoma lid and steam <b>15 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>. Remove Varoma and check mussels have all opened. If not, remove open mussels and transfer into a bowl, place Varoma back into position and steam for a further <b>5-10 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>. Remove Varoma, discard any mussels that remain closed, transfer open mussels into bowl and set aside. Strain the cooking liquid through a fine mesh sieve into another bowl and set aside.","Place oil, eschalots, garlic cloves and chilli (optional) into mixing bowl and chop <b>7 sec\/speed 5<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl using spatula.","Sauté <b>3 min\/120°C\/speed 1<b>.","Add wine (optional) and cherry tomatoes and cook <b>2 min\/100°C\/speed 1<b>.","Add tomato paste and reserved cooking liquid, adding water to reach 700 g, then bring to a boil <b>7 min\/100°C\/speed 1<b>.","Add salt and penne and cook for <b>time indicated on packet\/100°C\/\/speed <b> or until al dente. Meanwhile, remove mussels from opened shells, reserving some mussels in their shells to garnish and set aside.","Transfer pasta into a serving bowl, add reserved steamed mussels, stir to combine using spatula and drizzle with extra oil. Garnish with reserved chopped parsley and reserved mussels in their shells before serving."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["4 - 5 sprigs fresh flat-leaf parsley, leaves only","250 g water, plus extra as needed","1000 g fresh mussels, shells scrubbed and debearded","30 g extra virgin olive oil, plus extra for serving","30 g eschalots, cut into halves","3 garlic cloves","1 fresh red chilli, small, deseeded if preferred (optional)","50 g dry white wine              (optional)","120 g cherry tomatoes, cut into halves","40 - 50 g tomato paste","1 pinch salt","350 g penne pasta or similar short dried pasta"]}],"id":"r156319","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-IRNjk7kfh1c\/XZM0Y8jy5mI\/AAAAAAAAa8A\/o5n33SAA5qMi07jE6DOgrbptDV4b4SibgCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_xjUe52Hfgfhe8Eo9.png","title":"Penne with mussels","publishedAt":"2017-05-08T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"17 g","fat":"15 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"65 g","calories":"2011 kJ \/ 480 kcal"},"usefulItems":"fine mesh sieve, bowl, serving bowl","basicInfo":["easy","35m","1h 5m","4 portions"]}